      • constructMasterBootRecord

        public static MBR constructMasterBootRecord(Disk disk)
        Factory method for constructing an MBR for a Disk. During creation, the master boot record is read and parsed and its values are stored in the returned MBR instance.
        Parameters:
        disk - the Disk from which to read the master boot record
        Returns:
        an new MBR instance
